---
const GITHUB = "https://github.com/With-the-Ranks/Spoke";
const PULLS = "https://github.com/With-the-Ranks/Spoke/pulls";
---

<section
  class="bg-[#f0f0f0] bg-[radial-gradient(#e4e4e4_1.5px,transparent_1.5px)] bg-[length:8px_8px] px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-24 lg:px-8 lg:py-32"
  id="open-source"
>
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-[960px] flex-col gap-8">
    <div class="text-[#0a0908]">
      <h2 class="font-display text-5xl leading-none sm:text-7xl lg:text-[90px]">
        Spoke is 100% open source.
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4 font-sans text-xl leading-normal sm:text-2xl">
        <p>
          Spoke has been powering organizers for over a decade, including the
          Bernie Sanders 2020 presidential campaign that sent over 260 million
          messages.
        </p>
        <p>
          Building on the work of <span class="font-bold">MoveOn</span> and <span
            class="font-bold">Politics Rewired</span
          >, we're committed to maintaining and improving Spoke, keeping it open
          source and accessible to all.
          <p>
            If you'd like to host Spoke yourself, take a look at our FAQ on self
            hosting. Or, submit a{" "}
            <a
              class="font-bold text-[#1f2aff] underline"
              href={PULLS}
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              target="_blank"
            >
              pull request</a
            >{" "}
            to contribute to the code base and improve Spoke for everyone.
          </p>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a
      class="inline-flex w-fit items-center justify-center gap-4 rounded-lg border-2 border-[#0a0908]/20 bg-white px-8 py-6 font-sans text-2xl font-bold text-[#0a0908] no-underline shadow-none transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-px hover:brightness-105 hover:shadow-md focus-visible:-translate-y-px focus-visible:brightness-105 focus-visible:shadow-md"
      href={GITHUB}
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      target="_blank"
    >
      View on GitHub
      <img alt="" aria-hidden="true" class="h-6 w-[25px] shrink-0" height="24" src="/assets/spoke/icon-github.svg" width="25" />
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
